      "rationale": "Three-level mesh refinement study performed (coarse 4.2M, medium 8.7M, fine 16.1M elements). Richardson extrapolation yielded GCI of 3.8% on predicted hemolysis index at the highest-shear operating point. Fine mesh selected for all production runs. Discretization error criterion satisfied at Gradation 2."
