      "acceptanceCriteria": "MRL 2 accepts Gradation 1 for model form; selection of turbulence and hemolysis sub-models documented.",
      "rationale": "SST k-ω turbulence model selected based on published performance for rotating machinery hemolysis applications. Power-law hemolysis damage accumulation model (Giersiepen et al.) applied. Model form selection documented and justified by literature precedent. Formal model form uncertainty analysis not required at MRL 2."
